                            <span class="feature-info">인력 난 및 인건비 절감</span>
                            <span class="underline-line"></span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-item">
                        <div class="feature-text">
                            <span class="feature-title">단 7시간 명품 영업</span>
                            <span class="feature-info">짧고 굵은 고효율 매장 운영</span>
                            <span class="underline-line"></span>
